total_avilable_sql: select count(*) as total_available_count from etl.etl_data_load where  files_available_flag = 'Y' and job_id = 17
coa_available_sql: select count(*) as coa_available_count from etl.etl_data_load where  files_available_flag = 'Y' and data_source_code in ('A','D','E','L','O') and job_id = 17
